  "description": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 8\"><div class=\"layoutArea\"><div class=\"column\"><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">For your Orbital/Deep Space Settlement, roll d50 and pick 1-2 entries from the relevant column in the Oracle. A population of “Few” or “Dozens” is “Small”. The results are suggestions for the </span><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F5'\"><em>primary</em> </span><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">industries in the Settlement. <br /><br />“Subsistence” means that the Settlement has nothing that even looks like “industry” and is just trying to survive – frequently the situation in very small Settlements.</span></p></div></div></div>",
